data.description: A great opportunity to become a homeowner in this sold brick home, two bedrooms on the first level with a large living room decorative fireplace  connected to a large formal dinning room. Attic is full finished with one bedroom and a huge family room, newer windows, newer furnace and a/c. Great value for your money close to everything schools, highways shopping center and parks. Seller will take care of village's repairs if any.
